    <h1 class="serif" style="font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,48px);line-height:1.0;">Exam System &amp; Rules</h1>
    <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-60);margin-top:8px;">How CCSU LLB examination, credits, and promotion work</p>
